1. PROPOSAL DETAILS

Remove the no lockup and 1 day lockup options from the Vault encouraging people to lock their ember a longer time with higuer rewards.

 &nbsp; 

2. ECONOMIC IMPACT - Higher lockups will have higher APR, getting more EMBER out of circulation and possibly removing some sell presure. Also, it encourages long term actions because of the limited short-term staking options. 

 &nbsp; 

3. IMPACT ON USERS - Users will lose their short term staking option but long term users will be rewarded with higher APRs. 

 &nbsp; 

4. EXPECTED POSITIVE IMPACT - More tokens will be locked for a longer time because of higher APRs and less options. This will increase the long term supporters. 

 &nbsp; 

5. KNOWN POTENTIAL OR NEGATIVE DOWNSIDES - People refusing to move to longer lock times can run away from ember and create a momentum sell pressure.
